270
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:20,150
It'll be on the house.

271
00:21:20,150 --> 00:21:22,340
 Thank you. 

272
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:23,960
Hae Joon.

273
00:21:31,370 --> 00:21:33,180
Hae Joon.

274
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:35,030
It's all right.

275
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:37,970
