317
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:09,350
Did Ahjumma come to take you to Seoul?

318
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:11,180
Yes.

319
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:13,530
So what will you do?

320
00:24:13,530 --> 00:24:15,410
I'm not going.

321
00:24:15,410 --> 00:24:18,440
