but if you think about it, Seoul is actually very close–

335
00:25:05,730 --> 00:25:07,660
Joo Won.

336
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:08,990
Yes?

337
00:25:12,050 --> 00:25:14,150
Don't let me go.

338
00:25:15,650 --> 00:25:21,600
