339
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,370
Are you stupid?

340
00:25:25,370 --> 00:25:26,960
I feel that way, too.

341
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:29,050
I just tried acting tough.

342
00:25:29,050 --> 00:25:31,560
