348
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:56,470
- You can just hide your face? 
 - Yes.

349
00:26:09,010 --> 00:26:11,040
Did you speak with San Ha's mom?

350
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:15,550
Yes, I called her on my way here, but she didn't answer.

351
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:17,400
What about San Ha?

352
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:23,200
I plan to stop by the hospital later this evening.

353
00:26:26,350 --> 00:26:29,580
Why are you sitting down? Go to San Ha if you have the time to sit down.

354
00:26:29,580 --> 00:26:31,270
Let me catch my breath.

355
00:26:31,270 --> 00:26:33,780
I didn't have a single meal today.

356
00:26:37,760 --> 00:26:39,100
