362
00:26:57,310 --> 00:27:02,080
If you get married and get a new wife, and San Ha gets a stepmom,

363
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:06,320
in that case, you both might get closer to each other.

364
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:07,640
Look at you.

365
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:10,790
