431
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:48,300
I would've also considered that field if my grades weren't good enough for medical school.

432
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:50,700
- To-go? 
 - Yes.

433
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:55,580
Was that girl Hyungnim's younger sister?

434
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:56,910
What?

435
00:31:58,300 --> 00:31:59,530
Yes.

436
00:31:59,530 --> 00:32:04,210
