438
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:10,990
- That's true. 
 - Who went where?

439
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:12,830
San Ha.

440
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:15,490
His younger sister came to the hospital.

441
00:32:17,570 --> 00:32:20,600
