444
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:29,690
Hey, it'd be weirder if she didn't look dejected.

445
00:32:30,370 --> 00:32:32,790
Their mom must be having another hard time.

446
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:35,640
Chronic illnesses are hard on the family,

447
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:38,220
but San Ha's mother is...

448
00:32:38,910 --> 00:32:41,310
Do you know Ahjumma well?

449
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:43,470
As if I do.

450
00:32:43,470 --> 00:32:46,780
I just met her a couple of times at the hospital.

451
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:49,630
All the girls who liked Kim San Ha back in our department

452
00:32:49,630 --> 00:32:52,760
would remain dedicated even when he didn't look at them.

453
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:57,130
But one visit from his mom to the hospital, and they all dropped away.

454
00:32:57,130 --> 00:32:59,140
Including you.

455
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:02,620
I never liked Kim San Ha from the start.

456
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:04,340
I know everything.

457
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:08,710
After you broke up with Hae Joon, you went to San Ha like this.

458
00:33:08,710 --> 00:33:11,020
Hey, you'd better watch it today.

459
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:12,700
Kim San Ha seems to be in a bad mood.

460
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:15,800
- Fooling around will get you in trouble. 
 - Right?

461
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:20,020
